01:12:46.655 --> 01:12:47.739
You bunch of--

1045
01:12:47.822 --> 01:12:49.449
Aw. shit. man!

1046
01:12:50.200 --> 01:12:51.826
- Bear mace.
- Yeah. more. more!

1047
01:12:54.871 --> 01:12:57.791
- Yeah. more.
- Yeah. do you like that shit?

1048
01:12:57.874 --> 01:12:59.417
Yeah. that's right. bi--

1049
01:12:59.501 --> 01:13:01.253
Oh. goddamn it!

1050
01:13:01.336 --> 01:13:02.837
I'm gonna kill you!

1051
01:13:18.770 --> 01:13:21.147
I'm gonna fucking rip
your fucking head off!

1052
01:13:21.231 --> 01:13:22.232
Just...

1053
01:13:23.149 --> 01:13:24.192
die!

1054
01:13:45.589 --> 01:13:46.965
Ah. okay.

1055
01:13:53.096 --> 01:13:55.640
Good thinking with the mace.

1056
01:13:55.724 --> 01:13:56.725
Yeah.

1057
01:14:01.021 --> 01:14:02.063
Jesus!

1058
01:14:02.772 --> 01:14:04.065
Hell of a way to go.

1059
01:14:11.031 --> 01:14:12.240
What'd you set a timer for?

1060
01:14:13.533 --> 01:14:14.576
It was for your...

1061
01:14:15.368 --> 01:14:17.871
for your ETA or whatever.

1062
01:14:19.998 --> 01:14:21.916
I actually should pee. though.

1063
01:14:22.000 --> 01:14:23.126
Yeah.

1064
01:14:23.710 --> 01:14:24.961
Wait. what?

1065
01:14:28.798 --> 01:14:31.134
Who the fuck are these guys. anyway?

1066
01:14:31.718 --> 01:14:34.679
No idea. Huge <i>Home Alone</i> fans. apparently.

1067
01:14:40.810 --> 01:14:41.811
Hey...

1068
01:14:43.980 --> 01:14:46.191
thanks again for coming.

1069
01:14:47.150 --> 01:14:50.111
Yeah. well. what are friends for. right?

1070
01:14:52.322 --> 01:14:54.199
- Yeah. man.
- That being said.

1071
01:14:54.824 --> 01:14:56.868
I will testify against you if need be.

1072
01:14:56.951 --> 01:14:59.287
Yeah. no. no worries. I assumed.

1073
01:15:02.165 --> 01:15:03.625
Oh. shit. It's the cops.

1074
01:15:03.708 --> 01:15:07.003
Well. great. Tell them everything.
Let them go save her.

1075
01:15:07.087 --> 01:15:10.423
No. no. no. They're not gonna listen
to me. They think I'm in on this.

1076
01:15:10.507 --> 01:15:12.759
If I go out there.
they'll bring me to the station.

1077
01:15:12.842 --> 01:15:15.929
And by the time I can convince anybody
to go after Sherry. she'll be dead.

1078
01:15:18.181 --> 01:15:19.182
Wait a minute.

1079
01:15:20.183 --> 01:15:23.144
I think I have an idea. Your Harley--
it's still parked out front. yeah?

1080
01:15:23.228 --> 01:15:24.062
Yeah.

1081
01:15:24.896 --> 01:15:25.855
Sort of.

1082
01:15:26.856 --> 01:15:28.108
What do you mean "sort of"?

1083
01:15:32.904 --> 01:15:33.905
Nathan Caine!

1084
01:15:34.489 --> 01:15:37.367
I need you to come out the house
with your hands up.

1085
01:15:39.369 --> 01:15:41.746
Look. don't make this harder
than it has to be. okay?

1086
01:15:41.830 --> 01:15:43.957
This whole town's going to shit

1087
01:15:44.040 --> 01:15:46.668
'cause the Chargers
and the Clippers betrayed us.

1088
01:15:46.751 --> 01:15:48.545
Really? Now?

1089
01:15:49.212 --> 01:15:52.799
Seriously. Broke our heart for what? To be
second fiddle to the Rams and the Lakers?

1090
01:15:52.882 --> 01:15:54.676
Freeze! Freeze!

1091
01:15:56.386 --> 01:15:59.139
- Freeze! Freeze!
- Hey. stop! Stop! Shit.

1092
01:16:12.152 --> 01:16:14.821
- Wait. what is he doing?
- I don't know.

1093
01:16:17.907 --> 01:16:19.075
Hands!

1094
01:16:19.159 --> 01:16:21.035
Let me see your hands! Hands!

1095
01:16:27.000 --> 01:16:28.251
Shit.

1096
01:16:28.334 --> 01:16:29.669
Who the hell is this guy?

1097
01:16:29.753 --> 01:16:33.047
Ha. ha. ha! You've been deceived.
for I am not Nate!

1098
01:16:33.131 --> 01:16:34.132
Don't care.

1099
01:16:36.801 --> 01:16:39.763
But who you are is somebody

1100
01:16:40.346 --> 01:16:41.598
who's about to go to jail.

1101
01:16:41.681 --> 01:16:44.726
No. no. wait. wait! I can help you!
I know where Nate's going.

1102
01:16:44.809 --> 01:16:46.394
- Yeah? Start talking then.
- Okay. but

1103
01:16:46.478 --> 01:16:48.646
could we have a no-kicking policy
from this point on?

1104
01:16:48.730 --> 01:16:50.482
Where is he?

1105
01:17:03.369 --> 01:17:05.330
<i>All right. come on! Time to go!</i>

1106
01:17:10.543 --> 01:17:12.796
- Where is your jump suit?
- I'm not doing this. Simon.

1107
01:17:14.214 --> 01:17:15.715
Not doing what?

1108
01:17:16.716 --> 01:17:18.009
It's already done.

1109
01:17:19.719 --> 01:17:20.804
Can't do it.

1110
01:17:21.805 --> 01:17:22.931
Oh. fuck off.

1111
01:17:25.058 --> 01:17:27.352
Since when did you grow
a conscience anyway?

1112
01:17:28.561 --> 01:17:31.231
I mean. what about
all the other jobs we've done?

1113
01:17:31.314 --> 01:17:32.899
We've killed people before.

1114
01:17:32.982 --> 01:17:35.819
No. You've killed
people before. Simon. You.

1115
01:17:35.902 --> 01:17:37.362
Not me. I'm not like you.

1116
01:17:49.833 --> 01:17:54.170
You think all this fake remorse
is gonna save your soul? Hm?

1117
01:17:56.130 --> 01:17:57.423
It's bullshit...

1118
01:17:57.507 --> 01:17:58.925
Simon.

1119
01:18:00.218 --> 01:18:01.511
...and you know it.

1120
01:18:04.347 --> 01:18:05.515
Drop the gun!

1121
01:18:06.432 --> 01:18:07.684
Oh. my God. Nate.

1122
01:18:07.767 --> 01:18:09.269
I'm not gonna ask you again.

1123
01:18:10.687 --> 01:18:11.813
Okay.

1124
01:18:19.362 --> 01:18:20.655
You okay. Sherry?

1125
01:18:23.449 --> 01:18:24.367
Um...

1126
01:18:24.450 --> 01:18:25.785
I'm sorry.

1127
01:18:26.286 --> 01:18:27.412
who the fuck are you?

1128
01:18:28.746 --> 01:18:30.456
I'm the guy that killed your friends.

1129
01:18:32.125 --> 01:18:35.503
So if you don't want to wind up like them.
I suggest you let her go

1130
01:18:35.587 --> 01:18:37.046
and you get the hell out of here.

1131
01:18:39.132 --> 01:18:41.634
Oh. my God.

1132
01:18:42.802 --> 01:18:46.014
Oh. my fucking God.

1133
01:18:47.640 --> 01:18:49.058
Simon. don't.

1134
01:18:52.145 --> 01:18:55.148
You're the guy from the bank. right?

1135
01:18:59.319 --> 01:19:00.612
Okay.

1136
01:19:00.695 --> 01:19:03.907
This is legitimately the funniest thing
that's ever happened to me.

1137
01:19:04.866 --> 01:19:08.328
You've been tailing us
to try to save Sherry.

1138
01:19:09.329 --> 01:19:10.496
Is that right?

1139
01:19:13.708 --> 01:19:15.668
I hate to break it to you. bud. but...

1140
01:19:18.171 --> 01:19:19.881
she's my fucking sister.

1141
01:19:25.011 --> 01:19:27.680
She played you. man. Yeah.

1142
01:19:32.727 --> 01:19:35.855
You thought that she had feelings for you.

1143
01:19:35.939 --> 01:19:37.941
Stop. don't. Nate. I'm...

1144
01:19:39.317 --> 01:19:43.404
I'm so sorry. okay?
I never meant for you to...

1145
01:19:43.488 --> 01:19:46.908
Look. everything that happened between us.
I meant it. okay? It was real. I swear.

1146
01:19:46.991 --> 01:19:48.660
Oh. what a load of horseshit!

1147
01:19:49.202 --> 01:19:50.370
Look. man.

1148
01:19:50.453 --> 01:19:52.997
<i>you're pointing the gun
at the wrong bank robber. dude.</i>

1149
01:19:53.957 --> 01:19:55.959
You should be shooting her.

1150
01:19:57.460 --> 01:19:58.878
So. now listen.

1151
01:20:01.214 --> 01:20:03.758
Why don't you just
get out of here. man. Okay?

1152
01:20:03.841 --> 01:20:05.134
What are you doing?

1153
01:20:06.678 --> 01:20:08.888
Get yourself to the urgent care

1154
01:20:08.972 --> 01:20:12.308
- and just forget all about this.
- Simon. stop it.

1155
01:20:12.892 --> 01:20:13.768
Get over it.

1156
01:20:48.261 --> 01:20:52.432
I'll give it to you. bank boy.
You can take a punch.

1157
01:20:57.020 --> 01:20:58.813
Let's see how you do

1158
01:20:58.896 --> 01:21:01.024
under a little pressure.

1159
01:21:01.107 --> 01:21:02.608
Perfect.

1160
01:21:09.240 --> 01:21:10.950
Simon. stop it!

1161
01:21:12.368 --> 01:21:13.870
It's not fucking funny. Stop it!

1162
01:21:17.457 --> 01:21:18.458
Stop!

1163
01:21:21.544 --> 01:21:22.670
Stop!

1164
01:21:23.880 --> 01:21:26.132
- What the hell you doing?
- What are you doing?

1165
01:21:26.215 --> 01:21:28.968
- Are you just gonna crush his head?
- Well. he started it!

1166
01:21:31.554 --> 01:21:32.513
Just go.

1167
01:21:32.597 --> 01:21:35.892
Honestly. just go! Take the money and go!
I'm gonna stay with him.

1168
01:21:36.476 --> 01:21:39.187
- You're gonna stay with that guy?
- Yeah.

1169
01:21:39.687 --> 01:21:40.813
Sherry.

1170
01:21:42.482 --> 01:21:43.524
Come on!

1171
01:21:46.069 --> 01:21:48.029
I don't even know you anymore.

1172
01:21:52.075 --> 01:21:53.159
Fine.

1173
01:22:03.336 --> 01:22:05.171
- You won't do it.
- Yeah?

1174
01:22:05.671 --> 01:22:06.631
You sure?

1175
01:22:14.180 --> 01:22:16.599
You know what? You're right.

1176
01:22:17.183 --> 01:22:18.851
You don't know me anymore.

1177
01:22:28.986 --> 01:22:30.863
Got him! Moving in.

1178
01:22:33.533 --> 01:22:34.992
Hands! Hands up!

1179
01:22:35.576 --> 01:22:36.869
Get them on your head.

1180
01:22:42.792 --> 01:22:44.710
This one's cooked. Help this guy.

1181
01:22:49.132 --> 01:22:51.676
Damn. Vespa guy was right.
He's pretty beat up.

1182
01:22:52.552 --> 01:22:54.887
Yeah. well. good thing
we're here to save his ass.

1183
01:22:57.056 --> 01:22:59.267
You're lucky that
you got such a good friend.

1184
01:22:59.350 --> 01:23:00.935
Little too chatty for me. though.

1185
01:23:21.747 --> 01:23:24.500
Backup will be here in five.
They're still stretched thin.

1186
01:23:24.584 --> 01:23:26.127
Does that mean I can punch out now?

1187
01:23:26.210 --> 01:23:28.671
Wanda's gonna start
<i>It's a Wonderful Life</i> without me.

1188
01:23:28.754 --> 01:23:30.798
Yeah. we'll just get
the elves to do your paperwork.

1189
01:23:30.882 --> 01:23:33.009
Wouldn't that be amazing if we had--

1190
01:24:21.974 --> 01:24:23.684
Hey. hey.

1191
01:24:23.768 --> 01:24:25.394
Show me where you're hurt.

1192
01:24:29.232 --> 01:24:31.984
You're gonna be okay.
You just have to get to a hospital.

1193
01:24:32.068 --> 01:24:33.819
I'm gonna take your car and go after them.

1194
01:24:33.903 --> 01:24:35.780
Like hell! I'm not giving you my keys.

1195
01:24:37.865 --> 01:24:38.699
Sorry.

1196
01:24:40.034 --> 01:24:41.577
Don't worry. I'm gonna make sure--

1197
01:24:46.749 --> 01:24:48.209
You're really gonna shoot me?

1198
01:24:48.292 --> 01:24:50.169
I should. asshole.

1199
01:24:51.254 --> 01:24:53.381
But I won't. You're taking me with you.

1200
01:24:57.301 --> 01:24:58.302
Okay.

1201
01:25:07.228 --> 01:25:10.189
Uh. hey. hi. Could someone please tell me
what's going on?

1202
01:25:10.982 --> 01:25:14.068
- Go. go. go! We're gonna lose him!
- Yeah. don't worry.

1203
01:25:14.151 --> 01:25:15.444
I know where he's going.

1204
01:25:15.528 --> 01:25:18.114
Where who's going? Oh. we're on
a high-speed chase right now?

1205
01:25:27.748 --> 01:25:28.582
Fuck!

1206
01:25:41.470 --> 01:25:43.055
Oh. shit.

1207
01:25:49.687 --> 01:25:51.772
At this speed. you won't be able
to make any adjustments.

1208
01:25:51.856 --> 01:25:52.898
and I don't know how you drive--

1209
01:25:52.982 --> 01:25:54.108
School bus!

1210
01:26:14.462 --> 01:26:15.588
What the fuck?

1211
01:26:16.672 --> 01:26:17.673
You again?

1212
01:26:18.507 --> 01:26:19.842
Oh. Jesus Christ.

1213
01:26:42.114 --> 01:26:43.783
- Stroller!
- Yo!

1214
01:26:44.617 --> 01:26:47.411
What the fuck is wrong with you?

1215
01:26:47.495 --> 01:26:50.039
God. Jesus! Where'd you learn
to drive like this?

1216
01:26:50.122 --> 01:26:51.624
I used to boost cars.

1217
01:26:54.168 --> 01:26:55.795
What? I don't anymore!

1218
01:27:01.842 --> 01:27:03.761
Oh. I might be dying

1219
01:27:03.844 --> 01:27:05.388
but I'm gonna kill you first.

1220
01:27:23.155 --> 01:27:23.989
Oh. shit.

1221
01:27:25.241 --> 01:27:26.117
Fuck!

1222
01:27:33.541 --> 01:27:35.000
You fucking loser.

1223
01:27:39.380 --> 01:27:41.257
So where's this son of a bitch going?

1224
01:27:41.340 --> 01:27:42.675
He's headed to Pier 7.

1225
01:27:43.426 --> 01:27:44.385
What for?

1226
01:27:44.468 --> 01:27:46.971
There's a boat waiting.
It was gonna take us south.

1227
01:27:47.054 --> 01:27:49.140
- Taxi!
- I can see. thank you!

1228
01:28:00.985 --> 01:28:03.028
Hey. slow down! Stop! Stop!

1229
01:28:10.286 --> 01:28:11.620
You want to know something funny?

1230
01:28:11.704 --> 01:28:14.039
If you'd have just stayed in that bank.

1231
01:28:15.082 --> 01:28:17.209
Sherry would be right here
sitting next to me.

1232
01:28:20.296 --> 01:28:21.422
She'd be just fine.

1233
01:28:22.756 --> 01:28:24.800
But now?

1234
01:28:25.551 --> 01:28:26.635
Now...

1235
01:28:27.136 --> 01:28:28.554
I'm gonna hunt her ass down.

1236
01:28:29.388 --> 01:28:30.973
I promise you that.

1237
01:28:32.391 --> 01:28:33.392
Yeah. well...

1238
01:28:35.436 --> 01:28:37.146
if you do find Sherry...

1239
01:28:39.440 --> 01:28:41.066
I want you to tell her
something for me. okay?

1240
01:28:41.150 --> 01:28:42.651
Oh. God.

1241
01:28:44.862 --> 01:28:47.072
You are one sorry son of a bitch.

1242
01:28:47.156 --> 01:28:48.699
You know that?

1243
01:28:51.535 --> 01:28:53.537
Yeah. I know. right?

1244
01:28:54.580 --> 01:28:55.831
It's kind of my thing.

1245
01:28:56.832 --> 01:28:58.918
Listen. I want you to tell her

1246
01:29:00.794 --> 01:29:02.755
that even though we didn't spend
a lot of time together.

1247
01:29:04.215 --> 01:29:07.551
that I always felt like <i>we...</i>

1248
01:29:08.552 --> 01:29:10.513
could've gone...

1249
01:29:11.722 --> 01:29:12.556
What?

1250
01:29:14.683 --> 01:29:16.685
What'd you feel like?

1251
01:29:16.769 --> 01:29:18.687
What was that?

1252
01:29:18.771 --> 01:29:21.607
I can't fucking hear you.
You're mumbling. Speak up!

1253
01:29:21.690 --> 01:29:23.984
Oh. sorry. I'll try to be a little more

1254
01:29:24.068 --> 01:29:25.069
clear!

1255
01:31:09.381 --> 01:31:13.427
I like that you're making me earn it.
bank boy. but we got to wrap this up.

1256
01:31:16.430 --> 01:31:17.640
Let's go.

1257
01:31:18.474 --> 01:31:19.850
What?

1258
01:31:19.933 --> 01:31:21.060
Fuck. I can't.

1259
01:31:21.143 --> 01:31:22.436
I can't.

1260
01:31:24.438 --> 01:31:26.523
- I'm sorry. I have to go.
- Wait. wait.

1261
01:31:30.277 --> 01:31:32.196
God. I hope I live to regret this.

1262
01:31:33.906 --> 01:31:34.865
Take it.

1263
01:31:35.949 --> 01:31:38.577
That motherfucker shot my partner.

1264
01:31:41.372 --> 01:31:42.498
Don't miss.

1265
01:31:48.545 --> 01:31:50.381
- And you. out!
- Oh. okay.

1266
01:31:51.882 --> 01:31:52.883
Get her to a hospital.

1267
01:31:53.467 --> 01:31:54.426
- Sure. Yeah.
- Go.

1268
01:31:56.470 --> 01:31:58.639
Oh! God. that's a lot of blood.

1269
01:31:58.722 --> 01:32:00.974
At least it's not a stick shift.
am I right?

1270
01:32:01.058 --> 01:32:02.434
Sorry. Bleeding to death. Right.

1271
01:32:31.171 --> 01:32:33.215
End of the line. bank boy.

1272
01:33:03.829 --> 01:33:05.205
You always did fight dirty.

1273
01:33:14.089 --> 01:33:15.549
Sherry!

1274
01:33:16.633 --> 01:33:19.636
Looks like I finally found a way
to make you feel something. huh?

1275
01:34:02.721 --> 01:34:05.224
It's okay. I got you.

1276
01:34:08.268 --> 01:34:09.269
Hey. asshole.

1277
01:34:09.937 --> 01:34:11.063
Feel this.

1278
01:34:26.119 --> 01:34:27.955
Nate! Hey. Nate?

1279
01:34:28.789 --> 01:34:31.416
Nate. hey. Nate.

1280
01:34:32.167 --> 01:34:33.794
- Hi.
- Hey...

1281
01:34:34.336 --> 01:34:35.420
Sherry...

1282
01:34:37.798 --> 01:34:39.132
I love you.

1283
01:34:41.552 --> 01:34:43.387
You're really cool.

1284
01:34:47.391 --> 01:34:51.436
No. no. no. no! Hey! Hey!

1285
01:34:51.520 --> 01:34:53.021
Nate. please.

1286
01:34:53.105 --> 01:34:55.148
Help! We're over here! Please!

1287
01:34:57.025 --> 01:34:59.987
I'm so sorry. Nate. I'm so sorry.

1288
01:35:00.070 --> 01:35:02.906
I'm here. I'm right here.
I'm not going anywhere. I promise.

1289
01:35:03.699 --> 01:35:04.616
I'm sorry.

1290
01:35:07.160 --> 01:35:08.328
I'm sorry.

1291
01:35:45.449 --> 01:35:47.576
Hey. hey. hey.

1292
01:35:47.659 --> 01:35:49.494
There he is.

1293
01:35:49.578 --> 01:35:51.580
How you feeling. bud?

1294
01:35:51.663 --> 01:35:52.998
What happened?

1295
01:35:53.081 --> 01:35:56.585
Well. you've had some major blood loss.

1296
01:35:56.668 --> 01:35:58.670
And a heart attack.

1297
01:35:58.754 --> 01:35:59.963
And a brain hemorrhage.

1298
01:36:01.006 --> 01:36:02.299
And third-degree burns.

1299
01:36:02.841 --> 01:36:05.636
And a lot of broken bones.
But you're okay now!

1300
01:36:05.719 --> 01:36:07.638
It's a Christmas miracle.

1301
01:36:08.847 --> 01:36:10.265
It's Christmas?

1302
01:36:10.349 --> 01:36:13.685
It's actually January 11th.
You've been in a medically induced coma.

1303
01:36:13.769 --> 01:36:16.271
But still. you're alive!

1304
01:36:19.483 --> 01:36:22.444
Wait. Sherry. Is she okay?

1305
01:36:22.527 --> 01:36:25.822
Don't worry. Sherry's fine. She's okay.

1306
01:36:28.533 --> 01:36:29.993
- We meet again.
- Hey.

1307
01:36:30.077 --> 01:36:32.120
Hey! Look who's up.

1308
01:36:32.204 --> 01:36:33.330
Yep.

1309
01:36:33.413 --> 01:36:34.665
You look...

1310
01:36:36.917 --> 01:36:37.918
brave.

1311
01:36:38.502 --> 01:36:41.588
I'm glad you're up
because I just came from the courthouse.

1312
01:36:41.672 --> 01:36:44.257
You know. you're looking at
some pretty serious charges here.

1313
01:36:44.341 --> 01:36:47.052
Manslaughter. breaking and entering.
grand theft auto.

1314
01:36:47.135 --> 01:36:48.470
Yeah. those...

1315
01:36:49.554 --> 01:36:51.765
- Those sound really bad.
- Yeah. they are.

1316
01:36:51.848 --> 01:36:54.017
There's enough here to lock you up
until you're twice my age.

1317
01:36:55.185 --> 01:36:57.104
But you did save a cop's life.

1318
01:36:57.187 --> 01:37:00.607
And you also had some
pretty persuasive character witnesses.

1319
01:37:02.401 --> 01:37:05.028
Also. you're a white guy
who works for a bank. so...

1320
01:37:05.112 --> 01:37:08.657
the judge took it easy on you.
Six months house arrest.

1321
01:37:08.740 --> 01:37:10.200
Five years probation.

1322
01:37:11.118 --> 01:37:13.120
Get a lawyer to look at that.
but it's a pretty good deal.

1323
01:37:16.164 --> 01:37:18.250
Almost forgot the best part.

1324
01:37:20.544 --> 01:37:22.462
This is from Grace.

1325
01:37:24.464 --> 01:37:25.424
My daughter.

1326
01:37:31.430 --> 01:37:32.639
Take care. Nate.

1327
01:37:34.433 --> 01:37:35.726
Thank you. Detective.

1328
01:37:35.809 --> 01:37:37.144
Detective.

1329
01:37:46.611 --> 01:37:48.697
You're look-- Are you looking at the hand?

1330
01:37:48.780 --> 01:37:52.659
Oh. the hand? You mean
your burnt-up. crisped-up hand? Yeah.

1331
01:37:52.743 --> 01:37:54.953
I mean. it's jarring. for sure.

1332
01:37:55.037 --> 01:37:56.204
Is it the worst part?

1333
01:37:56.288 --> 01:37:59.958
I just think they shouldn't have to
dress it up all sexy. like in fishnets.

1334
01:38:00.042 --> 01:38:01.543
It's a skin graft.

1335
01:38:01.626 --> 01:38:05.589
- Look. I would get a glove personally.
- Okay.

1336
01:38:07.591 --> 01:38:08.967
<i>Prepare for pain.</i>

1337
01:38:09.968 --> 01:38:11.636
<i>This guy must not know
who he's dealing with.</i>

1338
01:38:11.720 --> 01:38:13.180
Okay. cast toxic cloud.

1339
01:38:13.263 --> 01:38:15.265
I'm equipping the black stone armor.
I'm going in.

1340
01:38:15.348 --> 01:38:18.185
<i>Hey. you're coming on Saturday. right?
It's a big birthday for me.</i>

1341
01:38:18.268 --> 01:38:21.688
Yeah. man. Wait.
it's not at a biker bar. is it?

1342
01:38:21.772 --> 01:38:23.482
<i>Aw. fuck you.</i>

1343
01:38:24.274 --> 01:38:25.942
Yeah. man. of course I'm gonna be there.

1344
01:38:29.362 --> 01:38:30.572
Oh. shit!

1345
01:38:30.655 --> 01:38:32.240
<i>Dude. just hold it
for a couple more minutes.</i>

1346
01:38:32.324 --> 01:38:34.576
- <i>This guy's almost dead.</i>
- No. dude. it's not that.

1347
01:38:34.659 --> 01:38:36.578
I actually have to get ready
for that dinner.

1348
01:38:36.661 --> 01:38:39.247
<i>Wow. You're ditching me to go on a date.</i>

1349
01:38:39.331 --> 01:38:41.500
I know. I know.
It's very cute and adorable.

1350
01:38:41.583 --> 01:38:42.876
and I will make this up to you later.

1351
01:38:42.959 --> 01:38:44.211
- Goodbye.
- <i>Wait. wait. wait--</i>

1352
01:38:47.881 --> 01:38:49.007
Hey...

1353
01:38:50.217 --> 01:38:53.053
I can't believe it's been a year
since our first date.

1354
01:38:53.637 --> 01:38:54.638
I am...

1355
01:38:55.138 --> 01:38:57.140
so happy I tried the pie.

1356
01:38:58.391 --> 01:38:59.643
Me too.

1357
01:39:00.519 --> 01:39:01.812
And. hey. you even wore your tie.

1358
01:39:01.895 --> 01:39:03.897
Yeah. You noticed. Yeah.

1359
01:39:03.980 --> 01:39:08.068
It took the dry cleaners a while
to get the blood stains out. but...

1360
01:39:08.151 --> 01:39:10.070
- you know. they managed.
- They did a good job.

1361
01:39:10.153 --> 01:39:11.571
Oh. wait...

1362
01:39:11.655 --> 01:39:12.989
Sorry. I almost forgot.

1363
01:39:18.453 --> 01:39:19.996
Oh. my God.

1364
01:39:21.832 --> 01:39:23.708
You finally figured out the ending.

1365
01:39:24.292 --> 01:39:27.963
Felt kind of weird
to have the knight rescuing the damsel.

1366
01:39:28.046 --> 01:39:30.966
So I had them. you know.
kind of saving each other.

1367
01:39:32.217 --> 01:39:33.260
It's perfect.

1368
01:39:34.344 --> 01:39:35.804
Hey!

1369
01:39:35.887 --> 01:39:37.264
Button that shirt up!

1370
01:39:37.347 --> 01:39:38.974
This ain't no conjugal visit. man.

1371
01:39:39.057 --> 01:39:41.852
Oh. sorry. No. this isn't
like a sex thing. This is...

1372
01:39:41.935 --> 01:39:44.271
- Uh-huh?
- Okay. yep. Got it.

1373
01:39:44.354 --> 01:39:46.523
And I know
that's not an open flame I'm seeing.

1374
01:39:46.606 --> 01:39:47.607
Nope. It's not.

1375
01:39:50.277 --> 01:39:51.236
Sorry.

1376
01:39:51.319 --> 01:39:53.697
- Don't play with me.
- I'm not trying to play with you. sir.

1377
01:39:53.780 --> 01:39:54.823
Just shh.

1378
01:39:54.906 --> 01:39:56.158
Is he new?

1379
01:39:56.241 --> 01:39:57.367
- Uh. no.
- He's intense.

1380
01:39:57.450 --> 01:40:00.078
- He's really intense.
- Yeah. they're strict here. It's jail.

1381
01:40:00.162 --> 01:40:01.663
Inmate 241. time's up.

1382
01:40:01.746 --> 01:40:04.416
- That's a tight 15 minutes. huh?
- Yeah.

1383
01:40:05.000 --> 01:40:07.836
At least we only have to put up with it
for another eight months.

1384
01:40:07.919 --> 01:40:10.881
Yeah. seven months. 19 days.
but who's counting?

1385
01:40:12.215 --> 01:40:13.967
Don't make me come over there!

1386
01:40:15.177 --> 01:40:17.304
- You're gonna get me in trouble.
- I'm so sorry.

1387
01:40:17.387 --> 01:40:19.848
- He's so intense.
- I know. I got to go.

1388
01:40:19.931 --> 01:40:20.807
Okay.

1389
01:40:24.436 --> 01:40:26.688
I'll see you soon.

1390
01:40:27.439 --> 01:40:28.440
Novocaine.

1390
